			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Mage summoned mask and belt/girdle works on any pet; the procs on the fists work once the pet is level 10 (not you, so the level 12 pet), and the blades when the pet is level 40.
<br />

<br />
Order is: focus items, hp, int.  You already have some hp, so I'd probably go Masklinn's route and get int to 200, then more hp.  If you were untwinked, I'd put hp ahead of int.
<br />

<br />
Re meleeing; melee to 30 if you do needlites, and you should.  If you don't do them, you'll stop doing it about 20, but your defense skill will suffer.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
